title: Ep. 642 - Is Jethalal Kidnapped? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal encounters two strangers who tried to steal gadgets from his godown. When he tries to fight them back, he gets a warning to step back or else he will be harmed. The police arrive and mistakes Jethalal for the thief. What will happen next?

title: Ep. 643 - Jethalal In Jail - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya, Sundar and everyone else decides to go to the police station and file a missing report of Jethalal. Will they be surprised when they visit the jail?

title: Ep. 644 - Will Daya's Plan Work? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya, Champaklal, Sundar, And Tapu make a plan when they got to know what is happening in the godown. Sundar and Champaklal take the lead and try to mislead one of the burglars. Will this plan work or they will fall in some danger?

title: Ep. 645 - Jethalal Tries To Hide Himself - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal finally enters society but tries to hide as soon as Iyer and Babita call him. Even after calling his name a number of times, Jethalal refuses to come out of the auto-rickshaw. What can be Jetahlal's reason for doing this?

title: Ep. 646 - Jethalal Blames Nattu Kaka - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: HJethalal is quite happy when Sundar leaves the house to go back to his house in Ahmedabad. But when Nattu Kaka enters the house, Jethalal tells him how unhappy he is to see him because he had to face this trouble all because of him.

title: Ep. 647 - A Banter Between Popatlal And Bhide - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal sees Bhide keeping the umbrella in the corner. But he is pissed with this behavior of Bhide. He shouts and asks him to pick it up as that is not the right place to throw it. Bhide feels offended and the banter starts between them.

title: Ep. 648 - Popatlal's Deep Chat With Champaklal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popaatlal meets Chaampaklal at his house and starts a conversation with him. He asks what can be the reason he is not yet married. Why is it difficult to find a bride. Will Popatlal ever get married?

title: Ep. 649 - Popatlal Organises A Surprise Party - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal decides to organize a surprise party at the society's Club House. He then visits everyone and invites them to be at the clubhouse exactly at 1:20 PM. Everyone gets curious to know what can be the reason for this party.

title: Ep. 650 - Popatlal Catches Bhide Red-Handed - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide, Jethalal, and others finally decide to cancel the plan of going to Popatlal's surprise party. Unfortunately, Popatlal hears everything while he was entering the room. He is heart-broken and blames Bhide for using his post's undue advantage.

title: Ep. 651 - Everyone Surprised With Popatlal's Surprise - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: So finally everyone gathers in the society's Club House. Everyone starts guessing among themselves as to what can be the surprise. But as soon as Popatlal reveals his surprise, everyone is surprised themselves.

title: Ep. 652 - The Umbrella's Birthday Celebration - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal keeps the birthday surprise for his umbrella who has been with him for over 10 years. Everyone is confused and cannot understand what is going on, but they try their best to be there in Popatlal's happiness.

title: Ep. 653 - The Party Comes To An Abrupt End - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After a lot of celebration, everyone sits down to relax as they are very much tired. But then suddenly, the police enter the Club House and asks everyone to stay quiet and stand in the same position. What are the Gokuldham society members accused of?

title: Ep. 654 - Popatlal's Umbrella Gets Stolen - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone including Popatlal are furious because someone broke Popatlal's umbrella after stealing it. Popatlal is in deep grief and wants the culprit to be punished. What will everyone do?

title: Ep. 655 - Everyone Consoles Popatlal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal forgives Jatayu for whatever he did and wins everyone's heart. But as soon as Jayanti, Jatayu's wife, thanks Popatlal and give her blessings to Popat's wife and kids, he gets offended and starts feeling sad for himself.

title: Ep. 656 - Bhide Becomes A Delivery Boy - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Madhvi gets an order for some 'papad' and snacks. She asks Bhide to help her, who is busy reading the newspaper for the past 1 hour. Then she asks him to deliver the order to a nearby neighbor. Will Bhide become Madhvi's delivery boy?
